    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>For press inquiries, product submission guidelines, corrections, or general questions, contact our editorial team at <strong>hello@gummy-guide.com</strong>. We respond to all inquiries within 48 business hours.</p>

    <p class="au-d">Last updated: March 2026</p>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>
